# Django Polls Tutorial (with Poetry)

This repository follows the official Django tutorial and implements the **Polls** app step by step, using **Poetry** for dependency management.

Official tutorial reference:  
https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.2/intro/tutorial01/

---

## ðŸ“¦ Requirements

- Ubuntu / Linux (tested on Ubuntu 24)
- Python 3.10+
- Poetry
- Django 5.2

## To run the project
- poetry run python manage.py makemigrations
- poetry run python manage.py migrate
- poetry run python manage.py runserver
- visit: http://127.0.0.1:8000/polls/
